Params: {3: 'Climbing onto the wall with her appendages, Yata checks the next waypoint. Valeria soon follows.'}
{2: 'Yata', 3: "I caught our rat's signal. This should be the right way."}
{2: 'Yata', 3: "This is a virtual space inside Gestalt. Your anti-materiel rifle isn't a data weapon."}
{2: 'Yata', 3: "And the data weapons we have here won't do from this range. Give up."}
{2: 'Yata', 3: "It's a long trek to the next waypoint. You'll never get there at your pace, need a ride?"}
